                        <TextArea editable="false" prefHeight="467.0" prefWidth="920.0" text="Project Bio v. 1.0&#10;&#10;This is a simple guideline on how to use the program.&#10;&#10;1) See shows &#10;&#10;1a. Shows can be seen in the show table located in the left part of the program. &#10;1b. The table displays all shows available in the cinema. &#10;1c. Each row in the table holds a movie, its showtime and which theater it runs in. &#10;&#10;2) Create a reservation&#10;&#10;2a. Mark the desired show on your left according to the customer request.&#10;2b. A map of the seats will appear on the screen under the &quot;Show Hall&quot; tab. &#10;2c. The seats will have different colours depending on their availability. &#10;2d. A seat is available for booking if it is green.&#10;2e. A seat is marked blue if a green seat is clicked on, which indicates that is is ready to be booked.&#10;2f. A seat is red if it has already been booked and can't be clicked on. &#10;2g. To complete a reservation, follow 2a and click on the desired seat (if green) followed by the reserve button in the lower right corner.&#10;&#10;3) Delete a reservation&#10;&#10;3a. Please enter the &quot;Reservations&quot; tab to see all existing reservations. These are lynced to a marked show in the show table. &#10;3b. Mark the desired reservation that is to be deleted and click &quot;Delete&quot; in the lower right corner of the program. &#10;&#10;4) Create several reservations&#10;&#10;4a. If several different customers want to make a reservation you will have to perform one reservation at the time.&#10;4b. If the samme customer wants to make several reservations to the same movie, it can be done in one reservation.&#10;4c. To complete 4b, mark the desired amount of seats in the desires location and follow 2g. &#10;&#10;Features available in Project Bio v. 2.0 (not released yet) &#10;&#10;Search functions&#10;- Retrieve a customer reservation using name and phone number &#10;- Find shows playing only on a specific day &#10;- Find shows with available seat(s) for a customer reservation&#10;&#10;Reservations&#10;- Create simultaneous reservations independent of customer information &#10;- Edit an existing reservation, workaround to avoid deleting the old reservation first and then registering new one &#10;&#10;Feel free to  contact us at tvao@itu.dk for further help...  &#10;" AnchorPane.bottomAnchor="0.0" AnchorPane.leftAnchor="0.0" AnchorPane.rightAnchor="0.0" AnchorPane.topAnchor="0.0" />
